{"word":"ἑορτάζω","slug":"ἑορτάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἑορτάζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἑορτή'><el>ἑορτή</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to keep festival</i> or <i>holiday</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to celebrate as</i> or <i>by a festival</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}